When I do that,

11:39.730 --> 11:41.430
you're gonna eat
the whole cookie

11:41.430 --> 11:42.870
as quickly as you can.
- [chuckles]

11:42.870 --> 11:45.570
- Just shove the whole cookie
in your mouth

11:45.570 --> 11:47.170
and then put your hand back.

11:47.170 --> 11:48.830
Okay?
- Okay.

11:48.830 --> 11:50.870
- It's important
that you put your hand back

11:50.870 --> 11:52.970
because there's two more
cookies coming.

11:52.970 --> 11:55.000
- Do I have to eat those, too?
- Yes. Yes.

11:55.000 --> 11:56.270
Just shove them in
your mouth and chew.

11:56.270 --> 11:57.800
- I feel like you should have
picked somebody else.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.030
- It'll be fine. It'll be fine.
- Okay.

11:59.030 --> 12:00.770
- So three cookies
in total, okay?

12:00.770 --> 12:02.700
- I was trying not
to do gluten.

12:02.700 --> 12:05.500
So I'm guessing this
is gonna be a cheat day.

12:05.500 --> 12:06.870
It's fine. It's fine.
- Yes. It's only three.

12:06.870 --> 12:08.200
It's only three.
- Oh, great.

12:08.200 --> 12:09.700
- It's important
that you listen

12:09.700 --> 12:10.970
to the instructions as well

12:10.970 --> 12:14.270
because you're going
to be wearing this.

12:14.270 --> 12:16.030
- [groans]
- It's a blindfold.

12:16.030 --> 12:18.270
- Oh.
- Do you mind?

12:18.270 --> 12:20.370
- I mean, it doesn't matter
if I do.

12:20.370 --> 12:22.770
So, okay.
[laughter]

12:24.430 --> 12:25.600
- Is that comfortable?

12:25.600 --> 12:27.900
- I mean, I've had more
comfortable, but sure.

12:27.900 --> 12:29.130
[laughter]

12:29.130 --> 12:31.230
- Can you see this?
Can you see anything?

12:31.230 --> 12:32.870
- I see a blindfold.

12:32.870 --> 12:35.030
- Perfect.
Okay, don't worry, Alyson.

12:35.030 --> 12:37.570
You can trust me.
- I don't think so.

