[light orchestral music]

12:44.170 --> 12:45.800
- I don't like the music.

12:45.800 --> 12:48.630
[laughter]

13:39.430 --> 13:41.430
[laughter]

13:41.430 --> 13:42.700
- You there, Alyson?

